        "condition_expr": "is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"TownFalkreathFaction\") or is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"GuardFactionFalkreath\")",
        "content": "Indara Caerellia works Corpselight Farm alongside her husband Mathies. A Breton woman, she carries the weight of losing their daughter Lavinia to the werewolf Sinding.",
