        "condition_expr": "is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"TownFalkreathFaction\") or is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"GuardFactionFalkreath\")",
        "content": "Festus Krex is an elderly mage and veteran member of the Dark Brotherhood in the Falkreath Sanctuary. Bitter, cynical, and endlessly sarcastic, he has served Sithis longer than most can remember.",
        "display_name": "Festus Krex - Dark Brotherhood Mage",
        "emotion": "",
        "importance": 0.6,
