        "content": "Gabriella is a Dunmer member of the Dark Brotherhood in Falkreath, one of Astrid's most trusted assassins. Seductive and deadly, she serves the Night Mother without question.",
        "display_name": "Gabriella - Dark Brotherhood Assassin",
        "emotion": "",
        "importance": 0.6,
        "knowledge_key": "falkreath.people.gabriella",
