        "condition_expr": "is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"TownFalkreathFaction\") or is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"GuardFactionFalkreath\")",
        "content": "Nazir is a Redguard member of the Dark Brotherhood who handles initiation contracts and administrative duties in the Falkreath Sanctuary. Practical and sardonic, he survives the Sanctuary's purge and carries on the Brotherhood's work.",
        "display_name": "Nazir - Dark Brotherhood Handler",
        "emotion": "",
        "importance": 0.65,
